article_id:1697,category_name:News,title_name:Announcing the Next Summon Showcase, Stirring Shadows!,image_path:,message:<div>A Summon Showcase, Stirring Shadows, kicks off at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1603087200"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">This summon showcase features the adventurers and dragons who were added in the previously held The Accursed Archives, Stirring Shadows (Part One), and Stirring Shadows (Part Two) summon showcases.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Appearance rates for featured adventurers and dragons will be boosted during this showcase!</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurers and dragons:</div><div>■Adventurers</div><div>5★ Lathna (shadow/lance)</div><div>5★ Curran (shadow/axe)</div><div>5★ Akasha (wind/staff)</div><div>5★ Heinwald (shadow/staff)</div><div><br></div><div>■Dragons</div><div>5★ Nyarlathotep (shadow)</div><div>5★ Hastur (wind)</div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for featured summons:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1603087200"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1603432799"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the featured adventurers and dragons below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurers:</div><div>
